Comment: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:31.73,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,isn't that... *realisation noise*
Comment: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:33.07,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:07.46,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Well, today was a waste of time.{lit. today was pointless/stupid}{alt: we sure got nothing done today}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:09.20,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Like every day?{lit. has there been a non-kudaranai day?}{alt: do we ever?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:10.50,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,I guess so.{lit. there hasn't, right...?}{alt: I don't think so}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:15.43,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,It's like they say: "Life's but a walking shadow, a poor player"!{that struts and frets his hour upon the stage and then is heard no more}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:16.50,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,What does {\i1}that{\i0} mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:17.73,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:20.18,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it mean life's pointless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:25.59,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,When I'm at home screaming, "Why am I alive?"\Nand stuff, my little brother always says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:27.60,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Is he trying to cheer you up or not?{lit. that's totally not consoling you}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:29.73,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Your little brother sounds like a clever kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:30.51,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,He sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:33.24,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:34.49,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:38.66,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Hey, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:41.38,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Don't just ignore your own flesh-and-blood sister!{lit. your blood-related one-and-only elder sister}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.38,0:00:42.88,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Way to disrespect our parents!{lit. you "lack of filial piety; disobedience to one's parents" person}{cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:45.18,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,I don't believe our parents are relevant here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:46.58,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Sure they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:48.42,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,You'll break Mom and Dad's hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:49.75,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Hanako, might he be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:51.78,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Yep! My little brother Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:52.93,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Isn't he a cutie?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:54.66,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,And he's super clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:57.01,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish {\i0}I{\i1} got to have a clever sibling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:00:58.25,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:00:59.76,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,P-Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.68,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Pl... Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:05.27,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:08.38,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,So Kasumi and Olivia exist after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.44,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:11.89,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,I thought they might be your imaginary friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:13.19,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,What? That's horrible!{rephrase}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:15.18,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Yep, we really exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:17.70,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Your sister's a very good friend to us.{this is just a generic polite Japanese thing to say, lit. we are always in her care}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:18.86,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:21.58,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's go home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:24.59,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,What? What's the problem?{lit. it's basically fine, isn't it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:26.53,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,We're going to the same place, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:27.96,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:35.63,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,There's a book I want to buy from the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:38.80,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Just get Maeda to buy it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:40.86,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,You're studying day in, day out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:43.20,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,You should come play outside once in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.14,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,You're studying day in, day out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.14,0:01:46.89,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when I have a test the next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:47.94,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:52.19,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,There's a park nearby. Let's go play there before we head home!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:53.37,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's a park here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:56.44,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,See? If you don't play, you don't learn anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:01:59.45,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,It's pretty empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.50,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,I haven't been to the park in forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:02.31,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:04.83,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,We used to play there all the time in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.80,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Whee!{she says yay but whee is what you say when you go down a slide in English so}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:10.04,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,And then {\i1}some{\i0} people will always be a feral child at heart.{lit. and then there are people who, no matter how much time passes, will be a feral child 野生児  / https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Feral_child}{i think the term's common enough to just use}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:12.79,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Ken! Come join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:17.30,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just sit here and read until she says it's time to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.55,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I even doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:28.55,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:31.65,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Look at these. Aren't they beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.69,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Marbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.54,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Yep. Found them when we were playing in the sandpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:39.37,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Look, there's a hole in the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:40.63,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Let's use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:43.37,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Come on, curve!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:47.24,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Nope, no luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:48.85,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Are you good at this kind of thing, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.48,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Ken-chan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.92,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Uh, no. I've never done it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:56.46,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll line them up again, so this time you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:03:01.50,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's see what you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.80,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.60,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.91,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.48,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,H-How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:19.90,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:23.82,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,If you apply horizontal rotational force, \Nthe marble's trajectory will curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:29.27,asobase-main,,2,2,0,,By analyzing the angle and size of the vectors,\Nyou can derive the path it'll take when you roll it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:33.59,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Then you adjust the follow-through to apply suitable rotation before the initial propulsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:36.37,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,O-Oh. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:38.19,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Did you get that, Kasumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.20,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,No, not a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.01,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:44.18,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,I didn't get a word of that,\Nbut it sure was impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:47.41,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,It was nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.33,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,You should give it a try too, Kasumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.02,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Can I? Okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:53.04,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.77,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:56.74,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Ken, time for round two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.32,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Uh... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.06,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.65,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess playing's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.57,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}not all that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:13.10,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,You just thought\N"Ah, this is heaven on earth", didn'tcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.08,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:21.43,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I was a tiny bit glad... that I had a big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.47,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:24.55,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not that I'll admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:27.39,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,All right, get ready. Now it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.30,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My dentures!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:39.48,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh my! Dear, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:40.91,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.58,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,How fast can you run 50 meters?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:46.66,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Just over nine seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.90,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Do it in five.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:49.66,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,To the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.56,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess I was right all along...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:57.12,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She really {\i0}does{\i1} ruin everything in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:59.13,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:00.92,asobase-main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asobi Asobase.
